00:32:41,125 --> 00:32:43,455
MANTENERME DESPIERTO

354
00:33:15,125 --> 00:33:16,875
¡SER VALIENTE!

355
00:33:34,166 --> 00:33:35,416
Háblame de Eleanor.

356
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:45,130
Era mandona como tú.

357
00:33:47,125 --> 00:33:48,325
Ya me cae bien.

358
00:33:52,250 --> 00:33:53,710
Odiaba leer.

359
00:33:56,666 --> 00:33:58,876
Solo le gustaba este poeta italiano,

360
00:33:59,875 --> 00:34:01,325
Cesare Pavese.

